        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p>
                <placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>May 8/67</date>
            </p>
            <p><addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>, Ed. Occident</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dr. Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Yours received in<lb/> reply would state that insert my
                adver<lb/>tisement but do not let it consume more<lb/> than 40 lines. If there is
                    <sic>to</sic> much matter<lb/> Cut it a little short. Send your Bill<lb/> to my
                office for collection. I shall<lb/> send you a sample set to your Place of<lb/>
                Business for the inspection of any who desire<lb/> to see them as I have done with
                all the<lb/> Jewish Newspaper Offices. The prospectus<lb/> sent you by
                    <persName>Miss Westernau</persName> are for the German<lb/> prints of the same
                picture. Mine are of American<lb/> production. And speak for themselves and I<lb/>
                have no doubt you believe in encouraging<lb/> home productions before going
                elsewhere. The<lb/> price to in proportion framed are much cheaper<lb/> than the
                European Prints being also photographs<lb/> The <sic>sett</sic> I shall send you
                tomorrow by</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>express. (As also a lot of pamphlet for<lb/> gratuitous circulation). I sell at<lb/>
                $12.00 the sett framed upon which I<lb/> allow a discount of $2.00 whilst some<lb/>
                I sell framed as low as $ 7.50.<lb/> You will also please insert in your<lb/> paper
                or magazine I should say the<lb/> following advertisement in some conspic<lb/>uous
                place - </p>
            <p>Wanted. Intelligent Jewish young<lb/> Men or Ladies to act as agents for<lb/> the
                Sale of the <sic>Celerated</sic> Pictures. Scenes<lb/> from Jewish Family Life of
                former days<lb/> A good opportunity. Apply or address</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">M. Samelson</persName>
                <placeName>98 Bowery</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">
                <placeName>N. Y.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>Send all claims to</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Respy Yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">M. Samelson</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>98 Bowery</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p>Will send sample pictures<lb/> by <hi rend="underline">Merchant Express</hi></p>
        </body>
